1. Select the file
2. Right click on the file
3. Select the Copy option
4. IDENTIFY THE LOCATION WHERE YOU WANT TO CREATE THE COPY
5. Go to that location
6. Right Click on that location
7. Select Paste option
8. Select the pasted file
9. Right click on pasted file
10. Select Rename
11. Change  the name
12. Press Enter

    NameOfTheClass nameOfTheNewCopy= new NameOfTheClass();